name: Car Repair details
query:
SELECT
    `tabCar Repair`.`customer_name` as `Customer Name:data:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`email` as `Email:data:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`phone` as `Phone:rating:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`reason_for_repair` as `Reason for Repair:data:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`car` as `Car:link:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`car_brand` as `Car Brand:link:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`car_manufacturing_year` as `Car Manufacturing Year:data:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`date` as `Repair Request Date :date:150`,
    `tabCar Repair`.`workflow_state` as `Status :link:150` 
    FROM    
        `tabCar Repair`
